<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id8e9dc8fc-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6" identifier="/us/usc/t22/s262p–4m"><num value="262p–4m">§ 262p–4m.</num><heading> Population, health, and nutrition programs</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of the Treasury shall instruct the United States Executive Director of the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development to urge the bank to support an increase in the amount the bank lends annually to support population, health, and nutrition programs of the borrower countries.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id8e9dc8fd-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/118/tXVI/s1618">Pub. L. 95–118, title XVI, § 1618</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/101/513/tV/s562/a/2">Pub. L. 101–513, title V, § 562(a)(2)</ref>, <date date="1990-11-05">Nov. 5, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/2033">104 Stat. 2033</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id8e9dc8fe-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id8e9dc8ff-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I87" topic="definitions" id="id8e9dc900-2930-11f1-8918-be39dde81dc6">
<heading class="centered smallCaps">Definitions</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">The definitions in <ref href="/us/usc/t22/s262p–5">section 262p–5 of this title</ref> apply to this section.</p>
</note>
</notes>
</section>
